MANUFACTURER_IDS_AUDIT.json
**/MANUFACTURER_IDS_AUDIT.json
*.analysis.json

# === Learnmode SVGs ===
**/learnmode.svg

# === KEEP these (required for App Store & Runtime): ===
# .homeychangelog.json - required
# drivers/*/assets/images/small.png - required
# drivers/*/assets/images/large.png - required  
# drivers/*/assets/images/xlarge.png - recommended
# drivers/*/assets/icon.svg - required
# data/fingerprints.json - REQUIRED AT RUNTIME (DeviceFingerprintDB.js lazy-loads it)
# driver-mapping-database.json - REQUIRED AT RUNTIME (DriverMappingLoader.js)
# lib/tuya/fingerprints.json - REQUIRED AT RUNTIME (tuya-engine)